# Drizzle migration snapshots are generated artifacts (drizzle-kit writes the full
# schema as JSON on every migration). They must stay tracked — db:generate diffs
# against them and a missing one silently corrupts the next migration — but they are
# not hand-reviewed. Mark generated so GitHub collapses them in PR diffs and drops
# them from language stats; `-diff` suppresses the multi-thousand-line textual diff.
# Scoped to *_snapshot.json only — _journal.json is tiny and worth reviewing (it
# names which migration was added).
packages/database/src/migrations/meta/*_snapshot.json linguist-generated=true -diff
